CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 27, 1958, pg. 2, reads: "Landlady's Home - Mrs. Sarah Langue, cited for violations of Allegheny County health regulations for properties on Manilla St., Hill District, lives in this home at 1083 Shady Ave., Squirrel Hill. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Large brick home with stone arches over door and second floor window and multiple dormers, 1083 Shady Avenue, Squirrel Hill
